title: Rigmar PS Karaoke CDG+MP3
description:
Pocket Songs are a Canadian Karaoke maker from the dawn of the Karaoke industry, outliving Pioneer and other classics.

Talking of classics they specialize in the big Hollywood show tunes and musicals with lots of hard to get show tunes in this package of over 1700 songs.   CDG+MP3 format with Audio from 128 kbps @ 41Khz or better for the new songs.  Please download in a timely manner.  You can view the plain text file outside the RAR for the Archive contents.  Thank you for seeding.

Rigmar Radio - Seeding to the World since 2004
